'''巴納德環'''（{{lang|en|'''Barnard's Loop''', Sh 2-276}}）是位於[[獵戶座|獵戶座]]的一個[[發射星雲|發射星雲]]。它是包含了[[馬頭星雲|馬頭星雲]]和明亮的[[猎户座大星云|猎户座大星云]]的[[獵戶座分子雲複合體|獵戶座分子雲複合體]]的一部分。巴納德環是一個巨大的[[弧|弧]]型結構，並且中心點大致位於猎户座大星云。獵戶座大星雲中的[[恆星|恆星]]可能與氣體被電離形成巴納德環的機制相關聯。

== 概要 ==
從地球看，巴納德環延伸超過600[[角分|角分]]，幾乎覆蓋了整個獵戶座。但其亮度極低，無法以肉眼看見，必須透過長時間曝光攝影方能清楚地看到這個星雲。1895年，美国天文学家[[愛德華·愛默生·巴納德|愛德華·愛默生·巴納德]]從经过長時間曝光的底片上發現了這個星雲。

目前的研究認為巴納德環距離地球為159[[秒差距|秒差距]]（518光年）<ref>{{cite journal |last=Wilson |first=B.A. |last2=Dame |first2=T.M. |last3=Masheder |first3=M.R.W. |last4=Thaddeus |first4=P. |title=A uniform CO survey of the molecular clouds in Orion and Monoceros |url=http://www.aanda.org/index.php?option=com_article&access=bibcode&Itemid=129&bibcode=2005A%2526A...430..523WFUL |journal=Astronomy and Astrophysics |volume=430 |date=2005 |pages=523–539 |doi=10.1051/0004-6361:20035943 |bibcode=2005A&A...430..523W |arxiv=astro-ph/0411089v1 |access-date=2018-03-09 |archive-date=2018-12-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181212161019/https://www.aanda.org/index.php?option=com_article&access=bibcode&Itemid=129&bibcode=2005A%2526A...430..523WFUL |dead-url=no }}</ref>或440 [[秒差距|秒差距]]（1434光年）<ref>{{cite journal |last=O'Dell |first=C.R. |last2=Ferland |first2=G.J. |last3=Porter |first3=R.L. |last4=van Hoof |first4=P.A.M. |title=Physical Conditions in Barnard's Loop, Components of the Orion-eridanus Bubble, and Implications for the Warm Ionized Medium Component of the Interstellar Medium |url=http://iopscience.iop.org/0004-637X/733/1/9/ |journal=The Astrophysical Journal |volume=733 |date=2011 |issue=1 |page=9 |doi=10.1088/0004-637X/733/1/9 |bibcode=2011ApJ...733....9O |arxiv=1103.2789 |access-date=2018-03-09 |archive-date=2020-06-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200614002619/https://hkvalidate.perfdrive.com/captcha?ssa=77a30235-2849-49ce-a2cb-9288785e954d&ssb=mm1g23l62ghb4fkhc5202e56b&ssc=http%3A%2F%2Fiopscience.iop.org%2F0004-637X%2F733%2F1%2F9%2F&ssd=089259321366103&sse=p%40inbcdjcplmbno&ssf=472a6228af1ce362a7956d7d1c5c014913fe83bc&ssg=cc89a1b2-2ae1-403a-84a6-cb023a08805b&ssh=15573c23-4bd6-4901-b7bf-6a74479c4eac&ssi=8040a36d-8427-4d8e-be81-2435d2d66040&ssj=aad763d8-9229-48cb-b623-27d3064fe1d8&ssk=support%40shieldsquare.com&ssl=285479646890&ssm=12132182359524199106499438025572&ssn=8bd2d857956398b733fa42a3b3301faecbfb305e0782-0b19-410f-87906d&sso=1674c605-974cb86aa42c164a4fc030fdd90d3be45c6e16645310a9e2&ssp=68894194071592097452159206293267675&ssq=06240359437825995811694378398564493472127&ssr=MjA3LjI0MS4yMzIuMTIx&sss=Chrome%2F5.0%20%28iPhone%3B%20U%3B%20CPU%20iPhone%20OS%203_0%20like%20Mac%20OS%20X%3B%20en-us%29%20AppleWebKit%2F528.18%20%28KHTML%2C%20like%20Gecko%29%20Version%2F4.0%20Mobile%2F7A341%20Safari%2F528.16&sst=python-requests%2F2.23.0&ssu=Mozilla%2F5.0%20%28compatible%3B%20Googlebot%2F2.1%3B%20+http%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fbot.html%29&ssv=v9sqr3mvqum1rr9&ssw=&ssx=608026040519026&ssy=naacjjegfadmkckeabbfmeecapapnkcfjfdmanca&ssz=c810c7a2c4215ec |dead-url=no }}</ref>，這取決於其直徑為100或300光年而定。巴納德環被認為可能源於約200萬年前的一次[[超新星|超新星]]爆炸。該次超新星也可能產生了數顆[[恆星運動學#速逃星|速逃星]]，包含[[御夫座AE|御夫座AE]]、[[天鸽座μ|天鸽座μ]]、[[白羊座53|白羊座53]]。一般認為前述恆星和巴納德環的前身恆星曾經是[[恆星系統|多合星系統]]的一部分，其中一顆恆星爆炸成為超新星<ref name="">{{cite web|url=http://www.daviddarling.info/encyclopedia/B/Barnards_Loop.html|publisher=David Darling|title=The Internet Encyclopedia of Science: Barnard's Loop (Sh 2-276)|accessdate=2008-04-22| archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20080312105026/http://www.daviddarling.info/encyclopedia/B/Barnards_Loop.html| archivedate= 12 March 2008 <!--DASHBot-->| deadurl= no}}</ref>。

雖然較早期的天文學家確實觀測到巴納德環這個亮度不高的星雲，但它的名稱來自於[[天文攝影|天文攝影]]的先驅[[愛德華·愛默生·巴納德|愛德華·愛默生·巴納德]]，他在1894年拍攝了這個星雲並發表了文章描述它<ref name="EEBarnard">{{cite journal|title=The great photographic nebula of Orion, encircling the belt and theta nebula|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_popular-astronomy_1894-11_2_3/page/n52|author=Barnard, E. E.|journal=Popular Astronomy|volume=2|pages=151–154|year=1894|bibcode=1894PA......2..151B}}</ref>。

